# Systematic Portfolio

## Overview
This repository tracks my personal research-driven portfolio with a focus on:
- Fundamental and quantitative analysis
- Factor-based investing
- Risk management and portfolio allocation

I aim to document my investment decisions and thought process in a clear, professional way.

## Current Holdings
