- Palantir (PLTR)
- FXAIX
- GLD
- NVDA
- QQQM
- RR
- SLV
- TTWO
- VOO

Each holding has a **dedicated memo** outlining:
- Thesis & rationale
- Risks
- Valuation considerations
- Future expectations

## Research & Learning
